query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('bioinformatics',
'core-graphics',
'custom-controls',
'dependencies',
'excel-2010',
'hashtable',
'modal-dialog',
'python',
'sorting',
'token',
'webbrowser-control');
